      <title>Northvolt 聘请咨询公司 Teneo 解决现金短缺问题</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/northvolt-hires-advisory-firm-teneo-to-tackle-cash-crunch</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，瑞典 Northvolt AB 已聘请咨询公司 Teneo 提供重组建议，包括如果这家债务支持电池制造商未能与贷方达成修改条款时的应急计划。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/northvolt-hires-advisory-firm-teneo-to-tackle-cash-crunch</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 24 Sep 2024 10:36:48 GMT</pubDate>
