    <item>
      <title>美联储降息致农业信贷银行加入异常资本争夺战</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/credit-agricole-joins-rush-for-unusual-capital-as-fed-cuts-rates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国农业信贷银行 (Credit Agricole SA) 计划通过发行一只只需十年偿还的债券来筹集资金，随着投资者希望利用美联储降息的机会，该行近期推出了一系列期限较长的债券工具。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/credit-agricole-joins-rush-for-unusual-capital-as-fed-cuts-rates</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 24 Sep 2024 10:04:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
