      <title>沙特债务狂潮来袭，沙特阿美计划通过债券发售筹集 30 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/aramco-taps-debt-markets-for-second-dollar-bond-sale-this-year</link>
      <description><![CDATA[沙特阿拉伯国有石油巨头希望通过两个月内第二次国际债券发售筹集 30 亿美元，这是该国今年债务狂潮中的最新一笔交易。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/aramco-taps-debt-markets-for-second-dollar-bond-sale-this-year</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 24 Sep 2024 05:59:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
